Package: oakdown
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown and thesisdown package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chester", "Ismay", email = "chester.ismay@gmail.com", role = c("cre")),
    person("Omkar", "Katta", email = "omkarakatta@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX and Word thesis templates from
    Reed College, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Omkar Katta <omkarakatta@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.2)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    here
Suggests:
    remotes,
    usethis
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - https://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
